# List of Number of Mishnayos by chapter / masechta

## Frage

<p>I'm looking for a list that enumerates the number of Mishnayos in each perek, as well as totals by masechta. Does anyone here know of such a list (or have the ability to quickly produce one)?</p>


## Antworten

### ✅ Antwort 1 (Score: 26)

<p>A Google spreadsheet with all that information (and more!) is available <a href="https://docs.google.com/spreadsheet/ccc?key=0AungNn-I1YDMdFR6R2UwWFl3MlZ1a2IwWXhTNmRQX0E" rel="noreferrer">here</a>.</p>

<p>A <a href="https://i.sstatic.net/PfG2b.png" rel="noreferrer">screenshot</a> of the more relevant part is clipped below:</p>

<p><img src="https://i.sstatic.net/PfG2b.png" alt="Excel Screenshot" title="Mishna Table"></p>


### Antwort 2 (Score: 4)

<p><a href="http://www.mishnasdura.org.il/?p=466" rel="nofollow">http://www.mishnasdura.org.il/?p=466</a>
This page has links to all the perokim and mishnayot in shass.</p>


